column5: Well the new boat seems to be cathing lots of Kings this spring ...
Sweet water wheels... Looks like a comfortable ride...
Cigar cowboy is having a good time! haha
Brilliant catch, what marina is that out of?
Nice!!   I'm guessing you're fishing the US side east of the bar (Wilson, etc)...  Our side this year has been extremely spotty..
WOW, way to go, that it a nice new ride.  Very impressed
Talk about being comfy while fishing. Nice boat,and I can see it also catches lots of fish. lol.
Looks like I should have run out deeper    Any news on if Weller is heating up yet?
I have not been off weller and the bar in 2 years ....i know there is lots of Cohos being caught that way ...
Nice ride Steve. What do you call the new barge? Fish magnet PI?
Great job man, I think I'll head down to Weller in a few weeks and hit the deep water!   Would like to boat a few spring chinnies before they move up and around to the north shore.
